<h3><a id="PPresentIssues">Present System & Issues</a></h3>
<h4>Present System</h4>
<ul>
	<li>At the University level, collections of data from the colleges are still carried out manually. </li>
	<li>Colleges furnish reports and information manually</li>
</ul>
<h4>Issues</h4>
<ul>
	<li>College directors do not get the overall picture on the progress status (both physical and financial). Therefore, it has been difficult for the college director to directly monitor and facilitate implementation.</li>
	<li>The Colleges are not able to have a reliable and consistent data sources due to lack of automatic updating system.</li>
	<li>The overall planning, implementation and monitoring at different levels become uncoordinated. Therefore, concerted efforts at different levels are missing to ensure smooth and well coordinated monitoring and facilitation of plan activities.</li>
	<li>Time consuming and prone to errors</li>
</ul>
